Package de.oth.blocklib.networking.messages.environment

This pacakge was created to show off the expandability of the Networking stack and especially its message types. Therefore, an (at the time) well-working functionality from a previous group was selected (the Environment topic) and networking support for this topic was added. E.g.: the server synchronizes the Day-/Nighttime to the connected clients now.
Since:
2020
Author:
Philipp Dormeier (HSP-SoSe 2020 Network)
